id: CMP-executor
kind: component
name: Executor
status: draft
conformance_level: structural
level: subsystem
path: CMP-mission-computer / CMP-executor
description: Translates mission commands from the planner into MAVLink message sequences. Owns pixel-to-GPS coordinate conversion (via MapCompositor) and enforces the 50 m altitude floor on goto_pixel and goto_waypoint. The loiter command bypasses the floor and issues its own altitude directly.
parent: CMP-mission-computer
satisfies: REQ-altitude-floor, REQ-pixel-coordinate-output
port: execution (provided IFC-mavlink-cmd)
events_scoped_here: VER-altitude-floor, VER-pixel-coordinate-output
